 By Johnbosco Agbakwuru – Abuja President Muhammadu Buhari has on behalf of the Federal Executive Council and all Nigerians, felicitated with former Head of State, Gen. Yakubu Gowon, on his 85th birthday, on October 19, 2019, describing him as a living legend and symbol of national unity. President Buhari said as Nigeria’s youngest leader since Independence, General Gowon’s visionary leadership style, wisdom and disciplined outlook kept the country as one, extolling the former Head of State for faith and steadfastness in God in times of adversity, and courageously pursuing the interest of majority Nigerians for a unified and stronger country. Continue reading Gowon @85: Symbol of national unity — Buhari at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard